{"text_id":165774,"tokens":["When"," it"," comes"," to"," making"," important"," decisions",","," it"," is"," often"," tempting"," to"," turn"," to"," a"," single"," trusted"," individual"," for"," advice","."," While"," this"," approach"," may"," provide"," a"," sense"," of"," simplicity"," and"," consistency",","," it"," also"," has"," the"," potential"," to"," limit"," the"," richness"," and"," diversity"," of"," perspectives"," that"," can"," inform"," and"," enrich"," the"," decision","-","making"," process","."," Seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," people",","," in"," contrast",","," can"," provide"," a"," more"," comprehensive"," and"," nuanced"," understanding"," of"," the"," issue"," at"," hand",","," leading"," to"," more"," well","-","informed"," and"," effective"," decisions",".","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," key"," benefits"," of"," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," people"," is"," the"," potential"," to"," gain"," exposure"," to"," a"," wider"," range"," of"," personal"," experiences","."," Each"," individual"," has"," a"," unique"," set"," of"," experiences"," and"," perspectives"," that"," can"," shape"," their"," perspective"," on"," a"," given"," issue","."," By"," gathering"," input"," from"," a"," diverse"," group"," of"," people",","," decision","-","makers"," can"," gain"," a"," more"," comprehensive"," understanding"," of"," the"," potential"," consequences"," and"," implications"," of"," a"," given"," course"," of"," action",".","\n\n","For"," example",","," consider"," a"," business"," owner"," who"," is"," considering"," expanding"," their"," operations"," into"," a"," new"," market","."," If"," they"," only"," seek"," advice"," from"," individuals"," who"," have"," previously"," worked"," in"," the"," same"," industry",","," they"," may"," miss"," out"," on"," valuable"," insights"," from"," those"," who"," have"," experience"," in"," related"," but"," distinct"," fields","."," By"," consulting"," with"," a"," diverse"," group"," of"," advisors",","," the"," business"," owner"," can"," gain"," a"," more"," nuanced"," understanding"," of"," the"," potential"," challenges"," and"," opportunities"," that"," may"," arise"," in"," the"," new"," market",","," leading"," to"," a"," more"," well","-","informed"," and"," successful"," expansion"," strategy",".","\n\n","Another"," benefit"," of"," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," people"," is"," the"," potential"," to"," minimize"," the"," impact"," of"," personal"," bias","."," Bias"," can"," take"," many"," forms",","," from"," unconscious"," assumptions"," and"," stereotypes"," to"," more"," overt"," forms"," of"," prejudice","."," Regardless"," of"," the"," form"," it"," takes",","," bias"," can"," have"," a"," significant"," impact"," on"," an"," individual","'","s"," perspective"," and"," decision","-","making"," process","."," By"," seeking"," input"," from"," a"," diverse"," group"," of"," advisors",","," decision","-","makers"," can"," help"," to"," offset"," the"," potential"," impact"," of"," personal"," bias"," and"," gain"," a"," more"," balanced"," and"," objective"," understanding"," of"," the"," issue"," at"," hand",".","\n\n","For"," instance",","," consider"," a"," hiring"," manager"," who"," is"," responsible"," for"," selecting"," a"," candidate"," for"," a"," critical"," role"," within"," their"," organization","."," If"," the"," hiring"," manager"," only"," seeks"," advice"," from"," individuals"," who"," share"," their"," own"," demographic"," characteristics"," or"," professional"," background",","," they"," may"," inadvertently"," overlook"," qualified"," candidates"," from"," under","represented"," groups","."," By"," consulting"," with"," a"," diverse"," group"," of"," advisors",","," the"," hiring"," manager"," can"," help"," to"," minimize"," the"," impact"," of"," personal"," bias"," and"," ensure"," that"," they"," are"," considering"," a"," wide"," range"," of"," qualified"," candidates",".","\n\n","In"," addition"," to"," personal"," experience"," and"," bias",","," diverse"," backgrounds"," can"," also"," play"," a"," role"," in"," shaping"," an"," individual","'","s"," perspective"," and"," decision","-","making"," process","."," Diverse"," backgrounds"," can"," encompass"," a"," wide"," range"," of"," factors",","," including"," cultural"," background",","," socioeconomic"," status",","," education",","," and"," professional"," experience","."," By"," seeking"," input"," from"," individuals"," with"," diverse"," backgrounds",","," decision","-","makers"," can"," gain"," a"," more"," comprehensive"," understanding"," of"," the"," potential"," impacts"," and"," implications"," of"," their"," decisions"," on"," a"," diverse"," range"," of"," stakeholders",".","\n\n","For"," example",","," consider"," a"," government"," official"," who"," is"," considering"," implementing"," a"," policy"," that"," will"," have"," a"," significant"," impact"," on"," a"," particular"," community","."," If"," the"," official"," only"," seeks"," advice"," from"," individuals"," who"," share"," their"," own"," cultural"," background"," and"," socioeconomic"," status",","," they"," may"," overlook"," the"," potential"," impact"," of"," the"," policy"," on"," individuals"," from"," different"," backgrounds","."," By"," consulting"," with"," a"," diverse"," group"," of"," advisors",","," the"," official"," can"," gain"," a"," more"," balanced"," and"," comprehensive"," understanding"," of"," the"," potential"," impact"," of"," the"," policy"," on"," a"," wide"," range"," of"," stakeholders",","," leading"," to"," a"," more"," well","-","informed"," and"," effective"," decision",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," people"," rather"," than"," just"," one"," person"," can"," provide"," a"," wide"," range"," of"," benefits"," when"," it"," comes"," to"," decision","-","making","."," By"," gathering"," input"," from"," a"," diverse"," group"," of"," advisors",","," decision","-","makers"," can"," gain"," a"," more"," comprehensive"," and"," nuanced"," understanding"," of"," the"," issue"," at"," hand",","," leading"," to"," more"," well","-","informed"," and"," effective"," decisions","."," Personal"," experience",","," bias",","," and"," diverse"," backgrounds"," can"," all"," shape"," an"," individual","'","s"," perspective"," and"," decision","-","making"," process",","," and"," seeking"," input"," from"," a"," diverse"," group"," of"," advisors"," can"," help"," to"," minimize"," the"," impact"," of"," these"," factors"," and"," ensure"," that"," decision","-","makers"," are"," considering"," a"," wide"," range"," of"," perspectives"," and"," potential"," consequences","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}